parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Takata airbag inflators can cause serious or fatal injuries in the event of a collision, as they may rupture and deploy with excessive force, sending shrapnel into the passenger compartment.
symptoms: None
as the issue is related to the potential failure of the airbag inflators in the event of a collision.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unavailability of replacement parts for the Takata airbag recall can leave vehicles in an unsafe condition, as the faulty airbag inflators may rupture and deploy with excessive force, sending shrapnel into the passenger compartment.
symptoms: None
as the issue is related to the unavailability of replacement parts for the Takata airbag recall.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A cracked dashboard and airbag compartment can compromise the safety of the vehicle's occupants, as the airbag may not deploy properly in the event of a collision.
symptoms: Cracks in the dashboard and airbag compartment.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause various malfunctions, including door lock failures, alarm system malfunctions, and engine stalling, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Doors lock or unlock randomly
alarm system goes off randomly
engine stalling
loss of power
and warning lights on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door lock actuator can cause the doors to lock or unlock randomly, which can lead to accidents or injuries, especially if a child or passenger is able to open the door while the vehicle is in motion.
symptoms: Doors lock or unlock randomly
doors fail to lock or unlock
and manual locking or unlocking is required.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Stalling and Loss of Power
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine stalling and loss of power can cause accidents or leave the driver stranded, especially if it occurs while driving at high speeds.
symptoms: Engine stalling
loss of power
and warning lights on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the hybrid system can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Vehicle stalling
loss of power
and warning lights on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the back-up sensor can cause accidents or injuries, especially if the driver is not aware of obstacles behind the vehicle.
symptoms: Back-up sensor fails to alert the driver of obstacles behind the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The electrical short in the instrument control panel can cause a fire, which can lead to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Flames and smoke emanating from the instrument control panel.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine stalling and hesitation can cause accidents, especially when the vehicle is in motion or at intersections, and can lead to rear-end collisions or other accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or hesitates when driving
especially when accelerating from a stop or turning; the check engine light may come on and then turn off; the vehicle may shake or make rattling noises.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The cracked dashboard can cause the airbag to deploy improperly in the event of an accident, potentially causing injury or death to occupants.
symptoms: The dashboard is cracked
especially around the airbag and instrument cluster; the cracks may be loud and rattling; the airbag cover may be popped up.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unexplained engine noise and acceleration can cause accidents, especially when the vehicle is in motion or at intersections, and can lead to rear-end collisions or other accidents.
symptoms: The engine makes unusual noises; the vehicle accelerates on its own; the check engine light may come on and then turn off.
